WEBVTT

00:00:00.036 --> 00:00:02.136 A:middle
This portion is the code editor.

00:00:02.186 --> 00:00:06.186 A:middle
The code editor allows you to
edit the files in your project.

00:00:06.236 --> 00:00:10.746 A:middle
To access options, such as
revealing a particular file

00:00:10.816 --> 00:00:13.526 A:middle
in the Explorer,
right-click the file tab.

00:00:13.576 --> 00:00:16.986 A:middle
The code editor will enhance
your coding experience

00:00:17.166 --> 00:00:20.766 A:middle
with syntax highlighting
and bracket auto completion

00:00:20.766 --> 00:00:25.626 A:middle
and will allow you to easily
indent or outdent your code.

00:00:25.716 --> 00:00:29.006 A:middle
You can open multiple
editors side by side,

00:00:29.096 --> 00:00:31.296 A:middle
both vertically and
horizontally.

00:00:31.396 --> 00:00:35.666 A:middle
You can resize and reorder the
editors as per your preference.

00:00:35.916 --> 00:00:39.636 A:middle
To reposition or resize
an editor, simply drag

00:00:39.636 --> 00:00:42.466 A:middle
and drop the tab to
the desired location.

